14:16.147 --> 14:18.434
Listen to me, Charlie.

14:19.359 --> 14:21.350
You're strong.

14:21.569 --> 14:24.106
You're so strong. You're like your mom.

14:25.031 --> 14:27.022
You can do this.

14:29.035 --> 14:30.776
You have to do this.

15:01.776 --> 15:04.359
At least wait till tomorrow.
You need to sleep.

15:04.570 --> 15:06.607
I'm wasting time.

15:10.410 --> 15:13.277
This doesn't make any sense.
Why would they take Danny?

15:13.496 --> 15:16.579
I don't know.
