25:39.163 --> 25:40.824
MAN 3:
Hey, blondie. Hey, blondie.

25:41.040 --> 25:42.371
MAN 4:
Come on over, talk to me.

25:42.541 --> 25:44.999
Come here, come here. Where you going?

25:48.672 --> 25:50.288
MAGGIE:
Excuse me.

25:51.133 --> 25:54.421
- Maybe you can help me.
- Oh, God, I hope so.

25:54.636 --> 25:56.297
We're looking for somebody.

25:56.472 --> 25:59.055
And that accent.
Lady, you are classing up the joint.

25:59.308 --> 26:02.141
